Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟纱季和好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来优香那家伙  明天要好好地报复她一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在在洗澡  过会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天  你有没有在天上飞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天上？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  真让人摸不着头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介说他看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四个女初中生在天上飞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介君？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还说其中一个是姐姐你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  现在的女初中生还能在天上飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我还真不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是看走眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果能飞的话  那我就每天飞去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  虽然我也这么说了 但是祐介实在太固执
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思问了你奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看到了  怎么办
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}喂  大树  你姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  她一早起来就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天她也来做广播体操的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也已经不是想要全勤奖的年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  飞天姐姐么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被看到了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才慌慌忙忙把我们召集过来么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么夏海你是怎么回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说人怎么可能在天上飞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大树君他相信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大树是相信了  但问题是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫做祐介的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个孩子直接看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那孩子把我们的事说出去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们真的飞起来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要对其他人保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我们再飞一次让别人看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为热门话题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在天空中飞翔的美少女四人组出现！」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就能偶像出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我认真地想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  优香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如果这个事情暴露出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会有可怕的黑衣男子过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们带到哪儿的研究设施里去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后被从头到脚到处检查  并且做这样那样的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会变成那样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能说完全没这个可能性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  我们能在天上飞以及夏海和纱季黏在一起都是神石大人的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么会受人关注的应该是神石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样会很麻烦  会很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  能为神社做宣传不是挺好嘛  会有很多客人来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要  我们家保持现在这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有机会能成为观光景点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是万一变成那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉神石就不会实现任何人的愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就好像是神石赐予我们的秘密礼物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被很多人知道的话  神石就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我不想让大家都知道我们在天上飞过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小孩子说的话也没有人会相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  那个叫做祐介的是怎么样一个孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个戴着眼镜 似乎很聪明的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且根据大树所说还非常顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之后会向大树打探一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也要小心  绝对不能再飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  那就这样  我早饭还没吃  肚子饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛子  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你们干的还真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要原样奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让优香和凛合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们今天一天就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去晨练吧  纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后关于你姐姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了  姐姐没有飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我是亲眼所见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在做白日梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的  我正在秘密基地读书  然后就看见四个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太  今天干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我家有亲戚要来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再这么纠缠不清我可要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中世纪的欧洲有许多人被怀疑是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到审判并且处了刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然里面大多数都是无辜的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定也有少数真的拥有不可思议的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说是超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中世纪的人们把她们称为魔女并恐惧着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大树的姐姐肯定拥有着魔女的血统…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适合而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  启太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  为什么我没能够更早发觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里再一次向神石许愿不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们俩分开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没分开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快分开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快分开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快分开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快分开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说没法取消许过的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  今天下午你有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去一次医院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲叫我去帮忙整理行李
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大树  你午饭已经吃好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大白天就开始打游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不和朋友一起玩么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天到晚在家里浑浑噩噩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假一转眼就会结束了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫上祐介君一起出去玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为是谁的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  帮我把水桶拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要站起来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微做一下准备运动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  凛子  叫你来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  因为我和优香是一心同体的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们关系还真是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香你要好好地感谢凛子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早  你们要的东西送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长  你来的真不是时候啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:11:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  吓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  是我太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  你都出血了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要消毒才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没伤得这么严重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母在那里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去借一点消毒药水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢  这都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村祐介
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫祐介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是祐介为什么要跟踪我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个有趣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会认为我是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你飞上天了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？  飞上天？  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和大树的姐姐在天上飞的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我亲眼看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和夏海确实是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那一定是祐介看错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去补习班了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是我看错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望着天空发呆的时候  睡着做梦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因为在哪里见过姐姐你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后睡迷糊记忆错乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为姐姐很普通嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我普通  真是失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的女生怎么会在天上飞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个城市偶尔是会飞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去向大树道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是都走到他家门口了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么也忘不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你们在天上飞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了这里就能放心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不太好吧  帮忙打扫到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事  也不能让凛一直帮忙下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是大树君么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  原来是优香和凛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被姐姐骂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是和朋友吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说中了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐被别人说成是魔女的话  确实会生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是因为那个而生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我完全搞不懂他为什么要撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介很喜欢UFO和超自然现象之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有时候会说些关于那方面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他并不是个会说谎的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:14:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就相信他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他说四个少女在那片天空中飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按常识来想  人怎么可能在天上飞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女无法在飞上天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在常识和朋友间做出选择的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介也一定是想让大树去相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡说八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是大树和祐介是因为我们才吵架的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法让他们和好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  再飞一次让他们看看不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样一来大树就知道祐介说的是真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香你又这样  事情闹大了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  那样说不定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连纱季也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不让大家知道  不引起骚动就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得祐介和大树是能保守秘密的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人能保守秘密的话就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介想用「那是白日梦」来说服自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那样是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是神石的事最好不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上  刚决定要保守神石这个秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这是我们和神石之间的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介认为我们是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就利用这点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是让我们做「魔女」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是没事  但是我每天都和大树在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他认为我是魔女的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我怎么继续过下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女就我一个人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作是我让大家飞起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  因为纱季要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要我离开了这个城市  那就一切就会恢复成以前的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先让大树和祐介都到那个看到我们飞的秘密基地里去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候会那样悄悄地把朋友带到天上去飞一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是魔女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能保守秘密的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就再飞一次给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证  不会对任何人说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天  在和前天一样的时间到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再在空中飞一次给你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候  你可以带一个想来的朋友一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我看的东西是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  真是让人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等着就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是去年文化祭搞化妆餐厅时穿过的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  有这个必要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设定是「靠小魔女纱季我们才飞上天」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在服装上也要让他们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身哦  纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  大树呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和祐介出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和计划的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介  昨天的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们飞上天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有好好地许愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们飞上天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞啊  飞啊  飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  我想飞上天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说实现过一次的愿望就不能再实现第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是昨天优香和凛不是黏在一起了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为对象不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天是夏海和纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神石真是太没常性了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能成为魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这个城市  到很远的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想在那之前让大树和祐介和好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么忙都没有帮上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我弟弟吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  你们打算怎么做出像是在天上飞的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  大树
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.24,0:23:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.18,0:23:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月23日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我觉得在下田  偶尔有少女在天上飞也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:24:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大树他们能和好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能自己解决问题  就说明他们还只是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是小孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.08,0:24:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当成小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  你比起米饭更喜欢零食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.31,0:24:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会忘带作业  又会找借口不上游泳课
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.89,0:24:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Four  Season的单曲发售前夜又会睡不着觉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算是大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做孩子有什么不好么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.73,0:24:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集夏色奇迹第四话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.13,0:24:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香向前冲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.33,0:24:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我和纱季不一样  只是个小孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

